  question: "What is the purpose of the Canvas Scaler component in Unity\u2019s UI
    system?"
  optionList:
  - It makes the UI scale based on the device's refresh rate.
  - It prevents the UI from scaling at all.
  - It controls how UI elements scale across different screen resolutions.
